					<img src="<%= asset_path 'tour_sms_short_code_messaging.jpg' %>" width="664" height="320" alt="SMS Short Code Messaging" />
					<p class="border normal">
Tatango offers your business access to a shared 5-digit short code, 68398.  This allows you to create SMS campaigns that work on all mobile carriers, at 
only a fraction of the cost of purchasing your own short code. Learn more about shared short code messaging below and the benefits it offers to your business.
					</p>
					
					<div>
						<div class="tour-right-left">
							<div class="tour-right-left-left">
								<h2>Easy to Remember Code</h2>
								<p>
Unlike regular 10-digit phone numbers, the Tatango phone number is 5 digits, making it significantly easier for consumers to remember and use on their own mobile devices. 
Use Tatango's short code 68398 to take your mobile marketing campaign to the next level.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div class="tour-right-left-right">
								<img src="<%= asset_path 'tour_sms_short_code_messaging_remember.jpg' %>" width="322" height="214" alt="Easy to Remember Code" />
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="tour-right-left">
							<div class="tour-right-left-left">
								<img src="<%= asset_path 'tour_sms_short_code_messaging_throughput.jpg' %>" width="322" height="214" alt="High Throughput" />
							</div>
							<div class="tour-right-left-right">
								<h2>High Throughput</h2>
								<p>
SMS short codes are built for high volumes of text messages. If it's essential for your text messages to arrive in a timely fashion on your consumers mobile phones, there's no better way then by using an SMS short code.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="tour-right-left">
							<div class="tour-right-left-left">
								<h2>Works on all carriers</h2>
								<p>
SMS short codes are the only wireless carrier approved method for advertising to consumers via text message. Because of this, the Tatango short code 68398 is approved to send SMS promotions to all U.S. wireless carriers.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div class="tour-right-left-right">
								<img src="<%= asset_path 'tour_sms_short_code_messaging_carriers.jpg' %>" width="322" height="214" alt="Works on all carriers" />
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="tour-right-left">
							<div class="tour-right-left-left">
								<img src="<%= asset_path 'tour_sms_short_code_messaging_optout.jpg' %>" width="322" height="214" alt="Opt-Out Capabilities" />
							</div>
							<div class="tour-right-left-right">
								<h2>Opt-Out Capabilities</h2>
								<p>
By using an SMS short code, mobile subscribers can <a href="/resources/video-stop-sms-messaging">easily opt-out</a> by replying to any SMS message with the word 'STOP'¬ù. This allows you to build a mobile subscriber database of consumers 
who wish to receive your SMS promotions, and allows the ones who don't an easy way to opt-out.
								</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="tour-right-left">
							<div class="tour-right-left-left">
								<h2>Shared Short Code</h2>
								<p>
Short codes are extremely expensive, but not anymore with the introduction of <a href="/resources/video-dedicated-shared-short-code">shared short codes</a>. Shared short codes allow multiple businesses to run SMS campaigns with just one short code. 
Get the power of SMS marketing for your business, without the cost of a dedicated short code by using Tatango. Want your own dedicated short code, <a href="/enterprise/dedicated-short-codes">learn more</a>.
								</p>
							</div>
							<div class="tour-right-left-right">
								<img src="<%= asset_path 'tour_sms_short_code_messaging_shared.jpg' %>" width="322" height="214" alt="Shared Short Code" />
