Want to make sure that every text message you send arrives successfully on a consumer's mobile phone? By using short code messaging, you'll know exactly what messages were delivered 
successfully to what mobile phones, as Tatango will be able to give you detailed reports for each SMS message and mobile subscriber.
								</p>
